# Security Rules

## MUST
- Enforce auth for private user APIs.
- Enforce admin guard for all `/api/admin/*`.
- Validate Telegram webhook secret.
- Rate-limit expensive APIs.
- Never commit secrets.
- Never log API keys, OAuth tokens, provider credentials, or Telegram secrets.
- Validate all API input.
- Store secrets in environment variables only.

## AUTH RULES
- Login required: AI Search, Watchlist, Bookmarks, Settings, Telegram bind/unbind.
- Admin required: all `/api/admin/*`.
- Webhook secret required: `POST /api/telegram/webhook`.

## FORBIDDEN
- No raw stack traces to frontend.
- No secrets in frontend bundle.
- No unvalidated external URLs.
- No admin write operation without audit log.
